Name: APS & DPS Prepressurization
checklistText:
<size=21>APS TEMP/PRESS PREPRESSURIZATION CHECK</size>

1.
PANEL 1:	HELIUM MON sel - PRESS 1
	MPS: HELIUM ind - 2800 to 3500 psia

2.
	HELIUM MON sel - PRESS 2
	MPS: HELIUM ind - 2800 to 3500 psia

3.
	PRPLNT TEMP/PRESS MON sw - ASC
	MPS:
		FUEL TEMP ind - 50 to 90 F
		OXID TEMP ind - 50 to 90 F
		FUEL PRESS ind - 108 to 172 psia
		OXID PRESS ind - 71 to 143 psia


<size=21>DPS TEMP/PRESS PREPRESSURIZATION CHECK</size>

1.
PANEL 1:	HELIUM MON sel - AMB PRESS
	MPS: HELIUM ind - 1490 to 1750 psia

2.	HELIUM MON sel - SUPCRIT PRESS
	MPS: HELIUM ind - 750 to 1320 psia

3.	HELIUM MON sel - AMB PRESS

4.	PRPLNT TEMP/PRESS MON sw - DES 2
	MPS:
		FUEL TEMP ind - 50 to 75 F
		OXID TEMP ind - 50 to 75 F
		FUEL PRESS ind - 70 to 122 psia
		OXID PRESS ind - 41 to 78 psia

5.	PRPLNT TEMP/PRESS MON sw - DES 1
	MPS:
		FUEL TEMP ind - 50 to 75 F
		OXID TEMP ind - 50 to 75 F
		FUEL PRESS ind - 70 to 122 psia
		OXID PRESS ind - 41 to 78 psia

6.	PRPLNT QTY MON sw - DES 1
	MPS:
		FUEL QUANTITY ind - 95% or less
		OXID QUANTITY ind - 95% or less

7.	PRPLNT QTY MON sw - DES 2
	Repeat as step 6

8.	PRPLNT QTY MIN sw - OFF

9.	PRPLNT TEMP/PRESS MON sw - DES 1

10.	DES He REG 1 tb - gray
	DES He REG 2 tb - gray
